column11: Past Changes of the configuration format can be found here
Setting Up Your Project A Symfony
Setting Up Your Project A Symfony

The SSH user name is the concatenation of your platforms unique ID
and the environment ID. The SSH hostname is ssh. prepended to the
hostname of your platforms region. I.E.:
[project-id]-[environment-id]@ssh.[server-region-hostname].
